---
import Layout from '../../../layouts/Layout.astro';
const lastUpdated = '2026-03-31';
---
<Layout title="CurrencySnap - Privacy Policy" description="Privacy Policy for CurrencySnap iOS app.">
  <div class="pt-24 min-h-screen">
    <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto px-4 py-16">
      <a href="/en/apps/currencysnap" class="text-sm text-text-muted hover:text-accent-purple transition-colors">&larr; CurrencySnap</a>

      <h1 class="text-3xl font-bold mt-8 mb-2 text-white">Privacy Policy</h1>
      <p class="text-text-muted mb-8">CurrencySnap - Camera Currency Converter</p>
      <p class="text-xs text-text-muted mb-8">Last updated: {lastUpdated}</p>

      <div class="prose prose-invert max-w-none space-y-6 text-text-muted">
        <p>OpenClaw ("we", "us", "our") built CurrencySnap as a free application. This page is used to inform users regarding our policies with the collection, use, and disclosure of personal information.</p>

        <h2 class="text-lg font-bold text-white mt-8 mb-3">Information Collection and Use</h2>
        <p>CurrencySnap does not collect or store personal data on external servers.</p>
        <ul class="list-disc pl-6 space-y-2">
          <li>No personal information is collected or transmitted</li>
          <li>No usage analytics or tracking</li>
          <li>No third-party analytics services</li>
          <li>No advertising identifiers</li>
          <li>No account or registration required</li>
        </ul>

        <h2 class="text-lg font-bold text-white mt-8 mb-3">Camera Access</h2>
        <p>CurrencySnap uses your device's camera to scan price tags and recognize numbers for currency conversion. Camera data is:</p>
        <ul class="list-disc pl-6 space-y-2">
          <li>Processed entirely on-device using Apple VisionKit OCR</li>
          <li>Never captured, stored, or saved as images</li>
          <li>Never transmitted to any server or third party</li>
          <li>Used only in real-time for text recognition, then immediately discarded</li>
        </ul>

        <h2 class="text-lg font-bold text-white mt-8 mb-3">Exchange Rate Data</h2>
        <p>CurrencySnap fetches exchange rates from public currency APIs to provide up-to-date conversions. Only a standard API request is made to retrieve rates — no personal data, device identifiers, or location information is sent. Rates are cached locally on your device for offline use.</p>

        <h2 class="text-lg font-bold text-white mt-8 mb-3">Data Storage</h2>
        <p>All favorite currency pairs, preferences, and cached exchange rates are stored locally on your device. This data never leaves your device and is not accessible to us or any third party.</p>

        <h2 class="text-lg font-bold text-white mt-8 mb-3">Third-Party Services</h2>
        <p>CurrencySnap uses public exchange rate APIs solely to fetch current currency rates. No personal data is transmitted in these requests.</p>

        <h2 class="text-lg font-bold text-white mt-8 mb-3">Children's Privacy</h2>
        <p>CurrencySnap does not collect any personal information from anyone, including children under the age of 13.</p>

        <h2 class="text-lg font-bold text-white mt-8 mb-3">Changes to This Privacy Policy</h2>
        <p>We may update our Privacy Policy from time to time. Changes will be posted on this page with an updated date.</p>

        <h2 class="text-lg font-bold text-white mt-8 mb-3">Contact Us</h2>
        <p>If you have any questions about this Privacy Policy, please contact us at <a href="mailto:support@mdk.guru" class="text-accent-purple hover:underline">support@mdk.guru</a>.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</Layout>
